Sender needs to make sure the uniqueness of the message Id, which is computed as hash(type.MessageOnly, sender, receiver, srcChainId, srcTxHash, dstChainId, message). If messages with the same Id are sent, only one of them will succeed at dst chain.. A fee is charged in the native gas token.
